' Created from repository source on 2026-05-27.
' Source checked: Flyway migrations under backend/src/main/resources/db/migration
' and JPA entities in adapter/out/persistence.
' Scope: conceptual domain overview, not a full ERD.

@startuml
title Domain Model Overview

left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype polyline
skinparam rectangle {
    BackgroundColor #E8F7FA
    BorderColor DarkSlateGray
    FontSize 12
}
skinparam ArrowColor #333333

rectangle "User & Identity\n----\nUser\nAdmin / Lecturer / Student\nDepartment\nStudentToken\nPasswordResetToken" as Identity

rectangle "Survey & Question\n----\nSurvey\nQuestion\nQuestionBank\nSurveyTemplate\nSurveyAssignment\nSurveyRecipient" as Survey

rectangle "Survey Response\n----\nSurveyResponse\nResponseDetail\nSubmitted recipient state" as Response

rectangle "Feedback\n----\nFeedback\nFeedbackResponse\nStudent-to-staff discussion" as Feedback

rectangle "Notification & Audit\n----\nNotification\nNotificationUser\nAuditLog" as NotifyAudit

rectangle "Report & AI Summary\n----\nSurveyAiSummary\nSummaryJob\nSourceState\nPendingChange\nThemeEmbedding" as AiReport

Identity --> Survey : admin creates\nstudent receives
Survey --> Response : collects answers
Identity --> Response : student submits
Identity --> Feedback : student/staff use
Survey --> NotifyAudit : publish/reminder events
Identity --> NotifyAudit : recipients and audit actor
Response --> AiReport : source comments
Survey --> AiReport : summary scope
Feedback --> NotifyAudit : response notification

note bottom of Survey
Recipient snapshot is generated when a survey is published.
This keeps assigned students stable after publication.
end note

note bottom of AiReport
AI summary and embedding data are modeled separately
to support refresh and incremental analysis.
end note

@enduml
